    "navbar": "Travel\nCuisine\nShopping\nStyle\nArts\nWellness",
    "text": "Travel\nCuisine\nShopping\nStyle\nArts\nWellness\nLOG IN\nSTAYS\nJust Like Heaven\nWith panoramic views of Lake Atitlán, Guatemala’s Casa Palopó is a far-flung delight.\nWORDS AND PHOTOGRAPHY BY SKYE PARROTT\nDESIGN\nBack to the Future\nLuxury watches embrace ’70s nostalgia and space-age glam.\nWORDS BY LAURIE KAHLE\nWINE AND SPIRITS\nInside the World of Champagne\nA writer travels to the storied wine region in France to clink glasses with leading producers and master the art of the blend.\nWORDS BY SIOBHAN REID, PHOTOGRAPHY BY DANIEL DORSA\nFASHION\nThe Hoodie of the Future\nBritish clothier Vollebak makes garments for today’s superhero.\nWORDS BY JEREMY MALMAN, ILLUSTRATION BY AHONEN & LAMBERG\nMOST READ\nEDITORS’ PICKS\nOur Favorite Travel Essentials of the Year\nEverything you need for your 2023 travel: our editors’ picks for on-the-road accessories that marry form and function.\nFOOD AND DRINK\nHow to Make the Perfect Cup of Italian Coffee\nUnpacking the history, allure, and ways to use the humble Moka pot.\nBODY AND MIND\nIn a Pickle\nWhy pickleball is the feel-good game craze we all need right now.\nFOOD AND DRINK\nThe Perfect Cup\nTerra Kaffe’s espresso machine elevates your morning ritual with the press of a button.\nEDITORS’ PICKS\nOur Favorite Shop-Small Destinations of the Year\nOur editors’ picks for special finds at unique stores.\nHOME\nOur Favorite Home Tech Items of the Year\nOur editors’ picks for the sleekest, most life-improving gadgets.\nGet Full Access\nLog in to Departures using your eligible Platinum Card® or Centurion® Card.*\nLOG IN\nNot a Card Member? Learn more.\n*Only U.S. Consumer or Business Platinum Card® Members or U.S. Consumer or Business Centurion® Members are eligible.\nSTYLE\nOur Favorite Menswear Items of the Year\nOur editors’ picks for the most stylish, essential menswear and accessories.\nWORDS BY T. COLE RACHEL, ILLUSTRATION BY AHONEN & LAMBERG\nTOP DESTINATIONS\nDESTINATIONS\nHill Country Is Redefining Texan Hospitality\nA new wave of hotels, wineries, and restaurants is transforming this rural region into a cultural oasis.\nWORDS BY KAYLA STEWART, PHOTOGRAPHY BY ALICE GAO\nSTAYS\nSublime Stays in Los Cabos and Todos Santos\nEscape the crowds of Mexico’s Baja peninsula at these one-of-a-kind properties.\nWORDS BY ELISSA POLLS, PHOTOGRAPHY BY SKYE PARROTT\nA PAID MOMENT WITH\nTHE AUSTRIAN TOURISM OFFICE\nThe Hidden Gems of Austria\nExperience nine off-the-beaten-path museums in Vienna and beyond that reveal the country’s contributions to global culture.\nWORDS BY DEPARTURES STUDIO84\nA PAID MOMENT WITH\nHILTON'S LUXURY BRANDS\nPulling Back the Sheets\nUnpack Waldorf Astoria Hotels & Resorts, Conrad Hotels & Resorts, and LXR Hotels & Resorts, shining a light on the details that define their diverse experiences.\nWORDS BY DEPARTURES STUDIO84\nSAVVY STYLE\nSTYLE\nOver the Shoulder\nThis Saint Laurent tote will keep you — and your most precious items — both stylish and warm.\nWORDS BY ALEX FRANK, PHOTOGRAPHY BY LEANDRO FARINA\nFASHION\nFashion for Good\nSky High Farm forges an alliance between fashion, art, and agriculture to tackle food insecurity — and innovates a philanthropic business model in the process.\nWORDS BY POLINA ARONOVA-CAHN, PHOTOGRAPHY BY RYAN MCGINLEY\nA PAID MOMENT WITH\nFREDERIQUE CONSTANT\nThe Watch Collector’s Best-Kept Secret\nGet to know Frederique Constant and find out why the brand’s signature Swiss-made timepieces deserve space in your collection.\nWORDS BY DEPARTURES STUDIO84\nDESIGN\nLuxury in Lacquer and Brass\nTurin-based design firm Marcante-Testa brings old-world Italian glamour into the present.\nWORDS BY MONICA KHEMSUROV, PHOTOGRAPHY BY CAROLA RIPAMONTI\nEXPLORE MORE\nFollow Us\nOriginal Stories.\nUnexpected Perspectives.\nLog in to Departures using your eligible Platinum Card® or Centurion® Card.*\nLOG IN\nNot a Card Member? Learn more.\n*Only U.S. Consumer or Business Platinum Card® Members or U.S. Consumer or Business Centurion® Members are eligible.\nAbout\nNewsletter\nArchive\nTerms of Use\nPrivacy Policy\nAdChoices\nFollow Us\nDepartures is a lifestyle resource for U.S. issued American Express Platinum Card® and Centurion® Members. While Departures is owned by American Express, the content is independently written by third party writers and creators. © 2022 American Express",
